{%- style -%}

.fc-about {
  width: 100%;
  padding: clamp(32px, 5vw, 64px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 64px);
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

#MainContent .fc-about-statement {
  font-family: var(--fc-font);
  font-size: clamp(18px, 3.5vw, 26px);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--fc-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.55;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  max-width: min(680px, 90vw);
  width: 100%;
  margin: 0;
  text-align: left;
  text-wrap: pretty;
}

{%- endstyle -%}

<div class="fc-about">

  <p class="fc-about-statement" lang="en">Finecoustic is an audio brand exploring how sound exists within everyday spaces. Developed through Fantech&rsquo;s experience in immersive technology and consumer electronics, Finecoustic focuses on a more specific direction, audio products with attention to how they look, feel, and sound with different settings &mdash; in rooms, on desks, or as a part of daily routines. We continue to refine our direction through each product we develop, learning how sound, design, and context come together in practice.</p>

</div>

